Class AutorunCommand

com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.commands.AutorunCommand
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAsciiCommand, ICommandParameters, IAsciiCommandResponder, IAsciiResponse
public class AutorunCommand extends AsciiSelfResponderCommandBase implements ICommandParameters
If supported by the reader, this command is used to read/write/delete/execute the AUTO.TXT file on the SD card, or the readers small, internal file. Be aware that this command cannot be used in an Autorun file. Note: The internal file, if present, is limited to 256 bytes.
